Cirrus is a powerful solution for managing configurations of network 
devices such as routers, switches, VPN concentrators, wireless access 
points and firewalls on complex, multi-vendor networks. Cirrus Configuration 
Management Software v3 makes it easy for network administrators to perform 
bulk changes, updates to IOSs and automatic backups of their network device 
configurations.
